column5: In no way is this a call out to you Dave.I thought you should know, that subway card I got from you at chapters in the fall, well it was not valid.Thank the fishing gods I had change in me pockets ,to pay for that delis sub.  No really,there  was no cash value to it   .Probly a mistake at the subway end.No biggie,just thought you should know, as I wouldnt want some poor starving sole,standing there in line then be turned away.LOL  This is a FYI.
That happens now and again. Had my tims card go from $10 to $0 in just 5 weeks with out using it. Got my money back as they made the mistake
Dang and the one I got in Sarnia had $20 on it I guess it pays to be first in line
Dave, PLEASE send him a new card or we'll hear about this until the lake freeze over...LOL
Theres ice here still on the bay,not for long,getting grey looking,not worth walking on. Gotz lots in me glass though,care to top it up?   .  No need Dave, as I said,FYI.
Don't ya just love it when you have a good tease on someone?
Dave,  Send Misfish a minnow bucket instead maybe.  Cheers, Ron...
LOL. I got mine the same time you got yours. Both mine and my daughter's worked.  We got them in 2010, so yours probably just expired Briam
Brian, Terry,  I don't understand???  Cheers, Ron...
